<h3>Service Area Pages</h3>
<p>Claude creates unique <a href="/blog/location-pages-seo/">location pages</a> for each service area. The key is providing specific local details to avoid duplicate content across cities.</p>
<p>Feed Claude local landmarks, neighborhood names, common customer pain points in each area, and relevant city statistics. The output reads like localized content rather than templated fill-in-the-blank pages.</p>
<h3>Review Response Generation</h3>
<p>Claude drafts personalized responses to customer reviews. Provide the review text and your business context. Claude generates a response that acknowledges specifics from the review rather than using generic templates.</p>
