<h2>FAQ</h2>
<p><strong>Is Claude better than ChatGPT for SEO?</strong></p>
<p>Claude produces more natural long-form content and handles larger context windows (200K vs 128K tokens). ChatGPT is better for keyword research with real-time web access. Most SEO professionals use both. Claude for content and analysis. <a href="/blog/chatgpt-for-seo-content/">ChatGPT for SEO</a> research and quick tasks.</p>
<p><strong>Can Claude replace an SEO agency?</strong></p>
<p>No. Claude is a tool, not a strategist. It executes tasks faster but does not set strategy, track results over time, or manage a complete SEO program. For done-for-you SEO at scale, services like Stacc handle the full pipeline for <a href="/pricing/">$99 per month</a>.</p>
<p><strong>What are the best Claude prompts for SEO?</strong></p>
<p>The best <a href="/blog/ai-prompts-seo-articles/">SEO prompts</a> include 5 elements: the task, target keyword, context data (pasted SERP results or competitor content), output format, and constraints (word count, tone, prohibited phrases). Generic prompts produce generic content. Specific prompts produce usable output.</p>
<p><strong>Does Google penalize content written with Claude?</strong></p>
<p>No. Google evaluates content quality, not authorship method. AI-generated content ranks when it meets E-E-A-T standards, provides genuine value, and satisfies search intent. Generic AI content fails because of quality issues, not because AI wrote it.</p>
<p><strong>How much does Claude cost for SEO work?</strong></p>
<p>Claude offers a free tier with limited usage. The Pro plan costs $20 per month with higher limits. The Team plan costs $30 per user per month. For heavy SEO use, the Pro plan handles most workflows. API access provides the most flexibility for <a href="/blog/automate-seo-workflow/">automated SEO workflows</a>.</p>
<p><strong>Can Claude write content that ranks on page 1?</strong></p>
<p>Yes, with the right workflow. Feed Claude real SERP data, competitor analysis, and brand voice guidelines. Provide E-E-A-T signals. Edit the output for original insights. Content following this process ranks comparably to human-written content because the quality signals match.</p>
<p>Claude AI for SEO is a multiplier, not a replacement. It makes good SEO professionals faster and more productive. It does not make SEO strategy unnecessary. The professionals who master the workflow of combining real data with Claude execution will outperform both the manual SEO teams and the prompt-and-publish crowd.</p>
